    "scene_1": {
      "id": "scene_1",
      "text": "Welcome to the Enchanted Museum! You stand at the entrance of a mysterious building that appears only once every hundred years.\n\nLegend says that those who explore it thoroughly will discover ancient secrets and magical artifacts.\n\n[DEMO: This story demonstrates ALL engine features]",
