    "scene_1_sign": {
      "id": "scene_1_sign",
      "text": "You approach the ornate sign. It's carved from ancient wood and glows with a faint magical aura.\n\n'Welcome, brave explorer. The museum holds three legendary artifacts: the Crystal Key, the Ancient Compass, and the Phoenix Feather. Collect them all to unlock the true ending.'",
