      "text": "You step into the Grand Hall. Marble columns stretch toward a vaulted ceiling painted with constellations. Display cases line the walls, each containing mysterious artifacts.\n\nTo your left is the Hall of Mirrors. To your right, the Ancient Library. Straight ahead, a locked door with three empty slots.",
