      "id": "scene_4_librarian",
      "text": "The Ancient Librarian looks up from her book. Her eyes are kind but ancient, as if she's seen countless centuries pass.\n\n'Welcome, seeker. The Phoenix Feather you seek is on the upper level. But be warned—it will only reveal itself to those who have proven their worth.'",
